INSERT INTO station_context (id, task_id, station_id, context_data)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
               RETURNING
                id as "id!: Uuid",
                task_id as "task_id!: Uuid",
                station_id as "station_id!: Uuid",
                context_data,
                created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
